## 7️⃣ 에러 처리

### 📋 HTTP 에러 응답

```go
func handleWithError(w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request) {
    // 404 Not Found
    if someCondition {
        http.NotFound(w, r)
        return
    }

    // 500 Internal Server Error
    if criticalError {
        http.Error(w, "Internal Server Error", http.StatusInternalServerError)
        return
    }

    // 200 OK (성공)
    w.WriteHeader(http.StatusOK)
    fmt.Fprint(w, "Success")
}

// HTTP 상태 코드
const (
    StatusOK                  = 200
    StatusCreated             = 201
    StatusBadRequest          = 400
    StatusUnauthorized        = 401
    StatusNotFound            = 404
    StatusInternalServerError = 500
)
```

